        <mxCell id="SbDRJDh3eLq2FMcqhdqS-87" value="Should just have different interfaces for Integrator and External Simulation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;In the Integrator interface, the simulation is the clock. In the External interface, there is a separate clock object." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
